@@TJvButtonStyle
<TITLE TJvButtonStyle type>
Summary
  Defines the look of the TJvNetscapeSplitter.
Description
  TJvButtonStyle is the type of the ButtonStyle property of TJvButtonStyle and defines the look of
  the splitter component.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvButtonStyle.bsNetscape
Looks like a splitter in Netscape Navigator.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvButtonStyle.bsWindows
Looks like a band with close, maximize and minimize buttons.

