@@TJvButtonWidthKind
<TITLE TJvButtonWidthKind type>
Summary
  Specifies how a size is to be interpreted.
Description
  TJvButtonWidthType is the type of the ButtonWidth property of a TJvNetscapeSplitter component.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvButtonWidthKind.btwPixels
The ButtonWidth value is in pixels.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvButtonWidthKind.btwPercentage
The ButtonWidth value is in percentage of the total width or height of th esplitter.

